 * Diagonal backward step.
 *
 * @param {{[x: number]: number}} V
 * @param {number} cMin
 * @param {number} cMax
 * @param {number} cmD
Assert(UB === D || V[cMax + 1] > V[cMax - 1]); // UB === D || xp > yp
